What is Lambda?
Serverless compute service.
Run code without managing servers.

Benefits:
No Server Management
Pay Per Execution
Auto Scaling
Event Driven

Supported Triggers:
S3
API Gateway
CloudWatch
DynamoDB

Architecture:
File Upload
     ↓
S3
     ↓
Lambda Trigger
     ↓
Process File

Real-Time Scenario:
Profile Picture Upload

User Uploads Image
        ↓
S3
        ↓
Lambda
        ↓
Resize Image
        ↓
Store Processed Image

Interview Question:

Why Lambda?
Ideal for event-driven workloads without server management.
